md-content
    header
        acme-navbar(creation-date="main.creationDate")
    .jumbotron
        h1 Homepage
        .lead
            img(src="assets/images/yeoman.png" alt="I'm Yeoman")
            | Always a pleasure scaffolding your apps
        md-button.md-raised.animated.infinite(ng-class="main.classAnimation" ng-click="main.showToastr()") Splendid Toastr
        p
            |With â™¥ thanks to the contributions of
            acme-malarkey(extra-values="['Yeoman', 'Gulp', 'Angular']")
    .techs(layout-align="center")
         md-card(ng-repeat="awesomeThing in main.awesomeThings | orderBy:'rank'")
            md-card-content
                img.pull-right(ng-src="assets/images/{{ awesomeThing.logo }}" alt="{{ awesomeThing.title }}")
                h3.md-title {{ awesomeThing.title }}
                p {{ awesomeThing.description }}
            .md-action-buttons
                md-button(ng-href="{{ awesomeThing.url }}") Website
